  "subject": "Update dependencies",
  "commit_message": "Update dependencies\n\n- Centralise dependency management in apex-pdp/pom.xml\n- Remove dependency versions managed by Spring Boot, e.g. kafka\n- Remove transitive dependency versions (e.g. exclusions on jruby)\n- Uplift all remaining dependencies to latest, e.g. jruby\n- Dependency uplifts for mvel2 and infinispan required config updates\n- Remove deprecated m2e eclipse profiles\n- Clean unused pom.xml.versionsBackup\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5592\nChange-Id: I16d4fcf360e7d14d453c05bcbfd645f77d86f01d\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\n",
